cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR 

The paper deals with medical image segmentation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed algorithm involves mathematical morphology and GrabCut, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for image processing. The paper also mentions a graphical user interface (GUI), which falls under computer graphics (cs.GR). Finally, the iterative refinement approach used in the algorithm can be seen as a form of machine learning or optimization, which is relevant to the subfields of machine learning (cs.LG).
